{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8fc31429e7","title":"给李公朴、闻一多家属的唁电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6413a7c629","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"d54451c79e","index":1,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":17,"articleId":"8fc31429e7"}],"tags":[{"id":"a7ea3bd8ce","name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"3adb125bd2","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":8,"text":"李公朴（一九○○——一九四六），江苏扬州人，一九四六年七月十一日在昆明被国民党特务暗杀。遇害前任中国民主同盟中央执行委员。闻一多（一八九九——一九四六），湖北浠水人，一九四六年七月十五日在昆明被国民党特务暗杀。遇害前任昆明西南联合大学教授、中国民主同盟中央执行委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"931870b734","type":"title","text":"给李公朴、闻一多家属的唁电","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"3adb125bd2","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"691b924e94","type":"paragraph","text":"昆明探转李公朴夫人张曼筠女士：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"06f3def8aa","type":"paragraph","text":"惊悉李公朴先生为反动派狙击逝世，无任悲愤！先生尽瘁救国事业与进步文化事业，威武不屈，富贵不淫，今为和平民主而遭反动派毒手，是为全国人民之损失，抑亦为先生不朽之光荣。全国人民必将以先生之死为警钟，奋起救国，即以自救。肃电致唁。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"186ef0cb72","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"b77ea247a5","type":"paragraph","text":"午元","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"a4cbdb7175","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"76667e317d","type":"paragraph","text":"昆明国立西南联大请转闻一多先生家属：","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"cbffee2e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"惊悉一多先生遇害，至深哀悼。先生为民主而奋斗，不屈不挠，可敬可佩。今遭奸人毒手，全国志士必将继先生遗志，再接再厉，务使民主事业克底于成。特电致唁。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"b664ae3a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"7047106a0f","type":"paragraph","text":"午篠","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"7c0bb7d7e5","type":"paragraph","text":"根据一九四六年七月十五日、十九日","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"},{"id":"5487783d35","type":"paragraph","text":"《解放日报》刊印。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7"}],"page":{"id":"8698399ad5","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"8fc31429e7","start":171,"end":172}}}},"__N_SSG":true}